Nemotron-3-Nano-30B-A3B (MoE hybrid Mamba+Attention) — 8xH200 single-node
========================================================================

Model: /cluster_public/miles_data/models/NVIDIA-Nemotron-3-Nano-30B-A3B-BF16
Runner: scripts/run-nemotron-3-nano-30b-a3b.sh
Acceptance: train_rollout_logprob_abs_diff < 0.02 across RL steps.

MoE config: 128 routed experts top-6, 1 shared expert, sigmoid routing with
expert_bias aux-free balancing, DeepSeek-V3-style routed_scaling_factor=2.5.

